quests.desc: It's time to explore the amazing world of TextWorld! Here is your task for today. Your first objective is to venture west. Then, ensure that the cuboid locker is open. After that, recover the type U keycard from the cuboid locker in the laundromat. And then, take a trip east. Once you do that, doublecheck that the type U gate is unlocked. And then, make sure that the type U gate is ajar. And then, attempt to head east. And then, move north. That done, recover the non-euclidean passkey from the floor of the closet. After that, Place the non-euclidean passkey into the non-euclidean safe to lock it. Got that? Good!

objective: Welcome to another profound episode of TextWorld! Here is your task for today. First of all, try to go to the west. With that accomplished, look and see that the cuboid locker is opened. And then, retrieve the type U keycard from the cuboid locker. After that, attempt to head east. With that done, make it so that the type U gate is unlocked. And then, open the type U gate. Then, go to the east. After that, make an effort to move north. That done, retrieve the non-euclidean passkey from the floor of the closet. After stealing the non-euclidean passkey, make it so the non-euclidean safe in the closet is locked. Once that's all handled, you can stop!
